# Migration Rules

## Naming

- Descriptive names: `create_posting_batches`, `add_status_to_posting_batches`
- One logical change per migration

## Financial Tables

- Use `NOT NULL` for required fields (amount, account_id, etc.)
- Add `CHECK` constraints for balance invariants where practical
- Consider `immutable` patterns for posted records (e.g. no UPDATE/DELETE on posted rows)

## Indexes

- Index foreign keys and status columns used in queries
- Composite indexes for common filter combinations (e.g. account_id + posted_at)
